oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.moac
Class MOACAttribute

java.lang.Object
  oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.moac.MOACAttribute
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class MOACAttribute
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Helper class to store MOAC Attributes MOAC Attributes stored are MOAC Init Flag MOAC Privilege Name MOAC Org Count MOAC Total Org Count [ count from FUN_ALL_BUSINESS_UNITS_V ] MOAC Org Id (null for Multi Org Mode ) MOAC Access Mode MOAC Default Org ID (From Profile option) MOAC User Guid from ApplSession MOAC Session ID from ApplSession
